replies.body:
Meh, league of cleavers broke like four champs. This patch we've got turrets with literally 0 armor and mr, soraka being the most cancerous thing since AP Yi, graves shitting on everyone in sight, blue wards all over the place, yasuo and trynd 1v5ing teams and coming out on top, all AP champs feeling awful to play, most junglers having to back after clearing two camps in the beginning, tanks being straight up unkillable because of the nerfs to armor pen and AP items in general, and buffs to tank items and masteries. 

But instead of all that people are crying about not having mana pots.

